org.cef.handler

Interface CefFocusHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CefClient, CefFocusHandlerAdapter 

    public interface CefFocusHandler
    Implement this interface to handle events related to focus. The methods of this class will be called on the UI thread.(实现此接口以处理与焦点相关的事件。该类的方法将在UI线程上调用。)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  CefFocusHandler.FocusSource
      Focus sources.(焦点来源。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onGotFocus(CefBrowser browser)
      Called when the browser component has received focus.(当浏览器组件接收到焦点时调用。)
      boolean onSetFocus(CefBrowser browser, CefFocusHandler.FocusSource source)
      Called when the browser component is requesting focus.(当浏览器组件请求焦点时调用。)
      void onTakeFocus(CefBrowser browser, boolean next)
      Called when the browser component is about to loose focus.(当浏览器组件即将失去焦点时调用。)

    • Method Detail

      • onGotFocus

        void onGotFocus(CefBrowser browser)
        Called when the browser component has received focus.(当浏览器组件接收到焦点时调用。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)

      • onSetFocus

        boolean onSetFocus(CefBrowser browser,
                   CefFocusHandler.FocusSource source)
        Called when the browser component is requesting focus.(当浏览器组件请求焦点时调用。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        source - indicates/ where the focus request is originating from.(source-指示焦点请求的来源。)
        Returns:
        false to allow the focus to be set or true to cancel setting the focus.(false表示允许设置焦点，true表示取消设置焦点。)

      • onTakeFocus

        void onTakeFocus(CefBrowser browser,
                 boolean next)
        Called when the browser component is about to loose focus. For instance, if focus was on the last HTML element and the user pressed the TAB key.(当浏览器组件即将失去焦点时调用。例如，如果焦点在最后一个HTML元素上，并且用户按下了TAB键。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        next - will be true if the browser is giving focus to the next component and false if the browser is giving focus to the previous component.(next-如果浏览器将焦点放在下一个组件上，则为true；如果浏览器将重点放在上一个组件，则为false。)
